# Triple QA gate

Three gates before merge. Skipping blocks merge.

1. Code evaluator — `SHIP | FIX | SPLIT`
2. Playwright MCP — `PASS | FAIL`
3. `make agent-verify` — `VERIFIED | FAILED`

Run 1+2 parallel, then 3. Merge only: **SHIP + PASS + VERIFIED**

After merge: [end-task-workflow](./end-task-workflow.mdc)

Full criteria: [docs/AGENT-DELIVERY.md](../../docs/AGENT-DELIVERY.md)

